<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Multi-Environment Infrastructure | Terraform + Ansible</title>
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body {
      font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);
      color:#e6edf3; min-height:100vh; padding:40px 20px;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    }
    .container { max-width:960px; width:100%; }
    .header { text-align:center; margin-bottom:40px; }
    .badge {
      display:inline-block; background:rgba(88,166,255,.15); color:#58a6ff;
      padding:6px 16px; border-radius:20px; font-size:.8rem; font-weight:600;
      letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:16px;
    }
    h1 { font-size:2.6rem; font-weight:800; margin-bottom:10px;
      background:linear-gradient(90deg,#58a6ff,#79c0ff,#a5d6ff);
      -webkit-background-clip:text; -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent; }
    .subtitle { color:#8b949e; font-size:1.1rem; }
    .grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr)); gap:20px; margin-bottom:40px; }
    .card {
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.05); backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); border-radius:16px; padding:24px;
      transition:transform .2s; }
    .card:hover { transform:translateY(-4px); }
    .card .label { color:#8b949e; font-size:.8rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .card .value { font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:700; color:#fff; word-break:break-all; }
    .pipeline {
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border-radius:16px; padding:30px; text-align:center; margin-bottom:30px; }
    .pipeline h2 { font-size:1.2rem; margin-bottom:20px; color:#79c0ff; }
    .flow { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:12px; }
    .step {
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1f6feb,#388bfd); padding:12px 20px;
      border-radius:10px; font-weight:600; font-size:.95rem; }
    .arrow { color:#58a6ff; font-size:1.4rem; }
    .stack { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; justify-content:center; }
    .tech { background:rgba(121,192,255,.12); border:1px solid rgba(121,192,255,.3);
      color:#79c0ff; padding:8px 16px; border-radius:8px; font-size:.85rem; font-weight:600; }
    .footer { text-align:center; color:#8b949e; margin-top:30px; font-size:.85rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <span class="badge">🚀 Provisioned with Infrastructure as Code</span>
      <h1>Multi-Environment Infrastructure</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Terraform + Ansible + AWS Secrets Manager</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><div class="label">Server</div><div class="value">{{ ansible_hostname }}</div></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="label">Private IP</div><div class="value">{{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</div></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="label">OS</div><div class="value">{{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</div></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="label">vCPUs / RAM</div><div class="value">{{ ansible_processor_vcpus }} / {{ (ansible_memtotal_mb/1024)|round(1) }} GB</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="pipeline">
      <h2>⚙️ Automation Pipeline</h2>
      <div class="flow">
        <span class="step">Terraform Provision</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step">Secrets Manager</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step">Ansible Configure</span>
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
        <span class="step">Live 🟢</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pipeline">
      <h2>🧩 Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="stack">
        <span class="tech">Terraform Workspaces</span>
        <span class="tech">Reusable Modules</span>
        <span class="tech">S3 Remote State</span>
        <span class="tech">DynamoDB Locking</span>
        <span class="tech">Ansible Roles</span>
        <span class="tech">AWS Secrets Manager</span>
        <span class="tech">IAM (no static keys)</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      Deployed by Ansible on {{ ansible_date_time.date }} · EC2 · ap-south-1
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

2. Add a task to the END of roles/webserver/tasks/main.yml:
- name: Deploy project landing page
  template:
    src: index.html.j2
    dest: /var/www/html/index.html
    owner: www-data
    group: www-data
    mode: "0644"
  notify: Restart nginx